  "english": [
    "<b>it is necessary to test them</b> to ensure that they do not burst when heated. If they are heated for the first time on a Festival, he will be thereby testing them, which is a prohibited labor. <b>And some say: Because it is necessary to harden them</b> by overheating them the first time to make them fit for use, which is considered preparing a vessel for use and is prohibited on a Festival.",
    "In relation to the above, the Gemara cites the following teaching: <b>We learned</b> in a mishna <b>there:</b> If one <b>trampled</b> fowl with his foot, <b>or threw it</b> against a <b>wall, or if an animal crushed it,</b> and it is <b>twitching</b> but cannot stand; <b>if</b> the animal <b>waited,</b> i.e., remained alive, <b>from</b> the <b>time</b> of the injury <b>until</b> the same <b>time</b> twenty-four hours later, <b>and he</b> subsequently <b>slaughtered it, it is kosher,</b> provided no other defect is found in it that would have caused it to die within twelve months, which would render it a <i>tereifa</i>. <b>Rabbi Elazar bar Yannai said in the name of Rabbi Elazar ben Antigonus: It requires examination</b> after slaughtering, to make sure it does not have a defect.",
    "In relation to the same issue, <b>Rabbi Yirmeya inquired of Rabbi Zeira: What is</b> the <i>halakha</i> <b>with regard to slaughtering it on a Festival? Do we assume on a Festival</b> that it has <b>a flaw or not?</b> In other words, may one rely on the assumption that a typical chicken has no defect? Or perhaps, since there is concern with regard to this particular bird and it requires examination, one should refrain from slaughtering it lest it turn out to be a <i>tereifa</i>. If so, he will have performed labor for no purpose.",
    "<b>He said to him</b> in response: <b>We</b> already <b>learned</b> that <b>one may not whiten tiles</b> in order to <b>roast on them. And we discussed it: What does he</b> thereby <b>do? And Rabba bar bar Ḥana said</b> that <b>Rabbi Yoḥanan said: Here we are dealing with new tiles,</b> and the Sages prohibited heating them <b>because</b> one first <b>needs to test them,</b> and they might crack when heated. If they were heated for the first time on a Festival and cracked, it would show that they were unfit for use, in which case heating them would have been an unnecessary labor. This indicates that one may not take a chance on a Festival with regard to something that might be flawed, and therefore a possible <i>tereifa</i> should be similarly prohibited.",
    "<b>He said to him:</b> This is no proof; <b>we learned</b> that the reason for <b>that</b> <i>halakha</i> is <b>because it is necessary to harden them</b> in order to make them into proper vessels. Therefore, there is no connection between making a vessel and conducting an examination. Consequently, there is no reason to prohibit the slaughter of such a chicken on a Festival.",
    "It <b>is taught</b> in a <i>baraita</i>: It is possible for several people to perform a single act of cooking on Shabbat, and all will be liable. How so? <b>One brings the fire, and one brings the wood, and one places the pot</b> on the stove, <b>and one brings the water</b> for the pot, <b>and one puts spices into</b> the food, <b>and one stirs</b> the pot; <b>they are all liable</b> for cooking. The Gemara wonders at this: <b>But wasn’t it taught</b> in a different <i>baraita</i> that <b>the last one is liable and all</b> the rest <b>are exempt?</b> The Gemara responds: This <b>is not difficult. This</b> case, where all are liable, is referring to a situation <b>in which he brought fire at the outset,</b> and therefore each of them performed part of the act of cooking; <b>that</b> case, where only the last one is liable, is referring to a situation <b>in which he brought fire at the end.</b> In that case, none of the earlier people performed any aspect of cooking at all, as the labor of cooking begins only from when fire is brought.",
    "The Gemara asks: <b>Granted, all of them performed an action</b> that constitutes a prohibited labor, and they are therefore partners in a prohibited act and the desecration of Shabbat. <b>But</b> the <b>one who places the pot</b> on the stove, <b>what</b> prohibited labor <b>has he performed? Rabbi Shimon ben Lakish said: Here we are dealing with a new pot, and due to whitening tiles they applied</b> the same prohibition to <b>it.</b> This means that one is not liable for cooking the food in the pot but for strengthening the pot itself, as is the case with heating tiles.",
    "§ <b>The Sages taught</b> in the <i>Tosefta</i>: <b>New ovens and stoves are similar to all vessels that</b> may be <b>carried in a courtyard</b> on a Festival, as one can place items on them. <b>However, one may not anoint them with oil, nor rub them with a rag, nor cool them with cold</b> liquids to <b>harden them</b>, as all these actions are considered preparing the vessel for use, which may not be done on a Festival. <b>And if</b> one did so <b>in order to bake</b> in the oven on the Festival itself, <b>this is permitted.</b>",
    "§ <b>The Sages taught</b> in the <i>Tosefta</i>: During a Festival <b>one may scald the head and the feet</b> of a slaughtered animal with hot water in order to remove the hairs from them, <b>and one may singe them in fire</b> for this purpose, <b>but one may not smear them with clay, nor earth, nor lime</b> in order to remove the hairs because this involves great effort, and it appears as though he is processing the skin. <b>And one may not shear</b> those hairs <b>with scissors,</b> as it appears as though he is performing the labor of shearing in an effort to obtain the hairs themselves.",
    "Similarly, <b>one may not trim</b> the top of the leaves connected to <b>the vegetable with its</b> special <b>shears, but one may prepare <i>kundas</i> and <i>akaviyot</i>,</b> bitter vegetables that can be eaten only after extensive cooking, although this involves great effort. <b>And one may kindle</b> fire <b>and bake in a large baker’s oven [<i>purnei</i>], and one may heat water in an <i>antikhi</i>,</b> a kind of large urn, <b>but one may not bake in a new baker’s oven lest it break.</b> If the oven cracks when heated because it was not properly made, one will have performed unnecessary work on a Festival.",
    "§ <b>The Sages taught</b> similarly in the <i>Tosefta</i>: <b>One may not blow</b> a fire <b>with bellows,</b> because this is the manner of a weekday activity, <b>but one may blow</b> a fire <b>with a tube,</b> in an unusual manner. <b>And one may not mend a skewer nor sharpen it. The Sages</b> further <b>taught</b> in the <i>Tosefta</i>: <b>One may not break a reed</b> in order to make a kind of skewer upon which <b>to roast salted</b> fish, <b>but one may crack a nut</b> covered <b>with a rag, and there is no concern lest it tear,</b> for even if this occurs, no prohibited labor has been performed.",
    "<strong>MISHNA:</strong> <b>And Rabbi Eliezer further stated</b> the following leniency: <b>A person may stand over</b> objects in <b>storage,</b> such as produce that he has for some reason previously set aside from use,"
  ],
  "gemara": [
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"sentence\" id=\"0\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>שֶׁצָּרִיךְ לְבׇדְקָן. וְאָמְרִי לַהּ: מִפְּנֵי שֶׁצָּרִיךְ",
      "segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "לְחׇסְמָן. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"1\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>תְּנַן הָתָם: דְּרָסָהּ אוֹ שֶׁטְּרָפָהּ בַּכּוֹתֶל,",
      "segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אוֹ שֶׁרְצָצַתָּה בְּהֵמָה וּמְפַרְכֶּסֶת, וְשָׁהֲתָה מֵעֵת",
      "segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "לְעֵת וּשְׁחָטָהּ — כְּשֵׁרָה. אָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-unknown\" data-sage-type=\"unknown\" title=\"Rabbi Elazar bar Yannai\" data-authority-id=\"21642\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Elazar bar Yannai\" data-name-he=\"רבי אלעזר בר ינאי\">רַבִּי אֶלְעָזָר בַּר יַנַּאי</span>",
      "segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "מִשּׁוּם <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rabbi Elazar ben Antigonus, second-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"426\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Elazar ben Antigonus\" data-name-he=\"רבי אלעזר בן אנטיגנוס\">רַבִּי אֶלְעָזָר בֶּן אַנְטִיגְנוֹס</span>: צְרִיכָה בְּדִיקָה.",
      "segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"sentence\" id=\"2\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>בְּעָא מִינֵּיהּ <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rabbi Yirmeya bar Taḥlifa II, third and fourth-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"1952\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Yirmeya bar Taḥlifa II\" data-name-he=\"רבי ירמיה\">רַבִּי יִרְמְיָה</span> <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rabbi Zeira I, third-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"1017\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Zeira I\" data-name-he=\"רַבִּי זֵירָא א׳\" data-resolution-rule=\"default_early_context\" data-resolution-explanation=\"Defaulted to the earlier figure because no later-context cue appeared nearby.\" data-resolution-reasons=\"[{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;heuristic&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;Default early context&quot;,&quot;detail&quot;:&quot;Defaulted to the earlier figure because no later-context cue appeared nearby.&quot;,&quot;attribution&quot;:&quot;Girsology disambiguation heuristics&quot;}]\">מֵרַבִּי זֵירָא</span>: מַהוּ לְשׇׁחְטָהּ",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "בְּיוֹם טוֹב? מִי מַחְזְקִינַן רֵעוּתָא בְּיוֹם טוֹב,",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אוֹ לָא? <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"3\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>אֲמַר לֵיהּ, תְּנֵינָא: אֵין מְלַבְּנִין אֶת",
      "segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "הָרְעָפִים לִצְלוֹת בָּהֶן. וַהֲוֵינַן בַּהּ: מַאי קָא עָבֵיד?",
      "segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "וְאָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rabba bar bar Ḥanna, third-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"2594\" data-full-name=\"Rabba bar bar Ḥanna\" data-name-he=\"רבה בר בר חנה\">רַבָּה בַּר בַּר חָנָה</span> אָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rabbi Yoḥanan II, second-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"1570\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Yoḥanan II\" data-name-he=\"רבי יוחנן\">רַבִּי יוֹחָנָן</span>: הָכָא",
      "segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "בִּרְעָפִים חֲדָשִׁים עָסְקִינַן, מִפְּנֵי שֶׁצָּרִיךְ לְבׇדְקָן.",
      "segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"sentence\" id=\"4\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>אֲמַר לֵיהּ: אֲנַן מִפְּנֵי שֶׁצָּרִיךְ לְחׇסְמָן מַתְנִינַן",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "לַהּ<span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-vilna-piska\" data-sugya-kind=\"vilna-piska\" data-sugya-id=\"190\" data-raw-symbol=\"׃\">׃</span> <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"5\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>תַּנְיָא: אֶחָד מֵבִיא אֶת הָאוּר, וְאֶחָד מֵבִיא",
      "segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אֶת הָעֵצִים, וְאֶחָד שׁוֹפֵת אֶת הַקְּדֵרָה, וְאֶחָד",
      "segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "מֵבִיא אֶת הַמַּיִם, וְאֶחָד נוֹתֵן בְּתוֹכוֹ תַּבְלִין,",
      "segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "וְאֶחָד מֵגִיס — כּוּלָּן חַיָּיבִין. וְהָתַנְיָא: אַחֲרוֹן חַיָּיב",
      "segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "וְכוּלָּן פְּטוּרִין! לָא קַשְׁיָא: הָא דְּאַיְיתִי אוּר",
      "segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "מֵעִיקָּרָא, הָא דְּאַיְיתִי אוּר לְבַסּוֹף. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"6\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>בִּשְׁלָמָא",
      "segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "כּוּלְּהוּ קָא עָבְדִי מַעֲשֶׂה, אֶלָּא שׁוֹפֵת אֶת",
      "segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "הַקְּדֵרָה מַאי קָא עָבֵיד? אָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rabbi Shimon ben Lakish, second-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"2879\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Shimon ben Lakish\" data-name-he=\"רבי שמעון בן לקיש\" data-crossline-group=\"name-ref-crossline-16852\">רַבִּי שִׁמְעוֹן בֶּן</span>",
      "segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rabbi Shimon ben Lakish, second-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"2879\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Shimon ben Lakish\" data-name-he=\"רבי שמעון בן לקיש\" data-crossline-group=\"name-ref-crossline-16852\">לָקִישׁ</span>: הָכָא בִּקְדֵרָה חֲדָשָׁה עָסְקִינַן, וּמִשּׁוּם",
      "segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "לִבּוּן רְעָפִים נָגְעוּ בָּהּ<span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-vilna-piska\" data-sugya-kind=\"vilna-piska\" data-sugya-id=\"191\" data-raw-symbol=\"׃\">׃</span> <span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-steinsaltz\" data-sugya-kind=\"steinsaltz\" data-sugya-id=\"174\" data-sentence-id=\"7\" data-steinsaltz-label=\"א\"></span> <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"7\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>תָּנוּ רַבָּנַן: תַּנּוּר וְכִירַיִם חֲדָשִׁים —",
      "segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "הֲרֵי הֵן כְּכׇל הַכֵּלִים הַנִּטָּלִין בֶּחָצֵר.",
      "segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אֲבָל אֵין סָכִין אוֹתָם שֶׁמֶן, וְאֵין טָשִׁין אוֹתָן",
      "segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "בְּמַטְלִית, וְאֵין מְפִיגִין אוֹתָן בְּצוֹנֵן כְּדֵי לְחׇסְמָן,",
      "segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "וְאִם בִּשְׁבִיל לֶאֱפוֹת — הֲרֵי זֶה מוּתָּר<span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-vilna-piska\" data-sugya-kind=\"vilna-piska\" data-sugya-id=\"192\" data-raw-symbol=\"׃\">׃</span> <span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-steinsaltz\" data-sugya-kind=\"steinsaltz\" data-sugya-id=\"175\" data-sentence-id=\"8\" data-steinsaltz-label=\"ב\"></span> <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"8\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>תָּנוּ רַבָּנַן:",
      "segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "מוֹלְגִין אֶת הָרֹאשׁ וְאֶת הָרַגְלַיִם וּמְהַבְהֲבִין",
      "segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אוֹתָן בָּאוּר, אֲבָל אֵין טוֹפְלִין אוֹתָם בְּחַרְסִית,",
      "segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "וְלֹא בַּאֲדָמָה, וְלֹא בְּסִיד. וְאֵין גּוֹזְזִין אוֹתָן",
      "segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "בְּמִסְפָּרַיִם. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"9\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>וְאֵין גּוֹזְזִין אֶת הַיָּרָק בַּתִּסְפּוֹרֶת שֶׁלּוֹ.",
      "segment_ids": [
        9
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אֲבָל מְתַקְּנִין אֶת הַקּוּנְדָּס וְאֶת הָעַכָּבִיּוֹת,",
      "segment_ids": [
        9
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "וּמַסִּיקִין וְאוֹפִין בְּפוּרְנִי, וּמְחַמִּין חַמִּין בְּאַנְטִיכִי,",
      "segment_ids": [
        9
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "וְאֵין אוֹפִין בְּפוּרְנִי חֲדָשָׁה שֶׁמָּא תִּפָּחֵת<span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-vilna-piska\" data-sugya-kind=\"vilna-piska\" data-sugya-id=\"193\" data-raw-symbol=\"׃\">׃</span> <span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-steinsaltz\" data-sugya-kind=\"steinsaltz\" data-sugya-id=\"176\" data-sentence-id=\"10\" data-steinsaltz-label=\"ג\"></span> <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"10\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>תָּנוּ רַבָּנַן:",
      "segment_ids": [
        10
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אֵין נוֹפְחִין בְּמַפּוּחַ, אֲבָל נוֹפְחִין בִּשְׁפוֹפֶרֶת.",
      "segment_ids": [
        10
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "וְאֵין מְתַקְּנִין אֶת הַשַּׁפּוּד, וְאֵין מְחַדְּדִין אוֹתוֹ. תָּנוּ",
      "segment_ids": [
        10
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "רַבָּנַן: אֵין מְפַצְּעִין אֶת הַקָּנֶה לִצְלוֹת בּוֹ",
      "segment_ids": [
        10
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "מָלִיחַ, אֲבָל מְפַצְּעִין אֶת הָאֱגוֹז בְּמַטְלִית,",
      "segment_ids": [
        10
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "וְאֵין חוֹשְׁשִׁין שֶׁמָּא תִּקָּרַע<span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-vilna-piska\" data-sugya-kind=\"vilna-piska\" data-sugya-id=\"194\" data-raw-symbol=\"׃\">׃</span> <span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-steinsaltz\" data-sugya-kind=\"steinsaltz\" data-sugya-id=\"177\" data-sentence-id=\"11\" data-steinsaltz-label=\"ד\"></span> <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"11\" type=\"start\">&star;</span><big><strong>מַתְנִי׳</strong></big> וְעוֹד",
      "segment_ids": [
        11
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rabbi Eliezer ben Hyrcanus, third-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"417\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Eliezer ben Hyrcanus\" data-name-he=\"רבי אליעזר בן הורקנוס\">רַבִּי אֱלִיעֶזֶר</span>: עוֹמֵד אָדָם עַל הַמּוּקְצֶה",
      "segment_ids": [
        11
      ]
    }
  ],
  "rashi": [
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>שֶׁצָּרִיךְ <span class=\"dh-divergent\">לבודקן</span></b> אם יוכלו לקבל לבונה הלכך ביו\"ט לא דלמא פקעי",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ואשתכח דטרח שלא לצורך: <b>וְאָמְרִי לַהּ: שֶׁצָּרִיךְ לְחׇסְמָן.</b> להקשותם",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 34a:1:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "בהסק ראשון הם מתחזקין ומתקשים הלכך אע\"ג דלצורך יו\"ט נמי",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 34a:1:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "הוא דהא צולין עליהם מיהו כיון דבהסק זה נעשה כלי אסור:",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 34a:1:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>תְּנַן הָתָם</b> באלו טרפות: <b>דרסה</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 34a:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b><span class=\"dh-divergent\">וטרפה</span> בַּכּוֹתֶל</b> אדם שדרס על העוף",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 34a:2:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "או שזרקו וחבטו בכותל: <b>אוֹ שֶׁרְצָצַתָּה</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 34a:2:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>בְּהֵמָה <span class=\"dh-divergent\">ומפרכס&amp;#x27</span></b> ואינה יכולה לעמוד:",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 34a:2:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>וְשָׁהֲתָה מֵעֵת לְעֵת</b> יום א' שלם",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 34a:2:4",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ושחטה כשרה: <b><span class=\"dh-divergent\">ה&quot;ג</span> <span class=\"dh-divergent\">א&quot;ר</span> <span class=\"dh-divergent\">אלעזר</span> בַּר</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 34a:2:5",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b><span class=\"dh-divergent\">ינאי</span> <span class=\"dh-divergent\">משום</span> <span class=\"dh-divergent\">ר&amp;quot;א</span> <span class=\"dh-divergent\">בן</span> <span class=\"dh-divergent\">אנטיגנוס</span> <span class=\"dh-divergent\">צריכה</span></b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 34a:2:5",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>בדיקה.</b> כי שהתה מעת לעת נמי",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 34a:2:5",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "צריכה בדיקה לאחר שחיטה שמא",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 34a:2:5",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "נשתברו רוב צלעותיה או נשברה",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 34a:2:5",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "השדרה ונפסק החוט שלה או אחד",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 34a:2:5",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "משאר מיני טרפות ושהייה דמעת",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 34a:2:5",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "לעת אצטריך דאי לא שהתה אע\"פ",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 34a:2:5",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "שבדקה ולא מצא סימן טרפות טרפה",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 34a:2:5",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "שזו היא אחת משמנה עשרה טרפות",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 34a:2:5",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ונקרא רסוקי אברים שאבריה",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 34a:2:5",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "מתפרקין כולן ואע\"פ שאין רושם",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 34a:2:5",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ניכר בה וזהו סימנה אם שהתה מעת",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 34a:2:5",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "לעת בידוע שלא נתרסקו אבריה",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 34a:2:5",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דקים להו לרבנן מסיני דרסוק אברים",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 34a:2:5",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "אינה חיה מעת לעת אבל שאר מיני",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 34a:2:5",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "טרפה חיה כל שנים עשר חדש: <b>מַהוּ</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 34a:3:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>לְשׇׁחְטָהּ <span class=\"dh-divergent\">ביו&quot;ט</span>.</b> מי חיישינן הואיל",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 34a:3:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "וצריכה בדיקה ואיתיליד בה רעותא:",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 34a:3:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>מי מחזקינן רעותא.</b> בגוה משום"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "חשש איסור מלאכה ביו\"ט דלמא"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "משתכח טרפה ונמצא שוחטה שלא"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "לצורך בשלמא שאר בהמות אע\"ג"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דמחמרינן אנפשין ובדקינן מיהו"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "סמכינן ארובא ורוב בהמות אינן"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "טרפות הכא מאי: <b>ביו&quot;ט.</b> כלומר משום"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "חומר מלאכה ביו\"ט: <b>מִפְּנֵי שֶׁצָּרִיךְ</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 34a:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>לבדקן.</b> וחיישינן דלמא פקעי אלמא",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 34a:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "מחזקינן רעותא משום חומר יו\"ט",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 34a:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "שלא ללבנן: <b>מִפְּנֵי שֶׁצָּרִיךְ לְחׇסְמָן.</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 34a:5:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ולא משום חשש פקיעה אלא דודאי",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 34a:5:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "משוי ליה מנע בהסק זה: <b>שׁוֹפֵת</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 34a:6:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>אֶת הַקְּדֵרָה</b> מושיבה רקנית על",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 34a:6:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "האור: <b>מֵגִיס</b> מנער בכף שקורין",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 34a:6:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "קומיבר\"א: <b>כּוּלָּן חַיָּיבִין.</b> מביא את",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 34a:6:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "האור משום מבעיר את הגחלת",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 34a:6:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דכשהוא מוליכה היא מתלבנה מרוח",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 34a:6:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "הליכתו ומביא את העצים לאור משום",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 34a:6:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "מבעיר שופת קדרה לקמיה מפרש",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 34a:6:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "מאי עביד נותן מים ותבלין ומגיס",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 34a:6:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "משום מבשל שאף הוא אב מלאכה:",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 34a:6:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>דְּאַיְיתִי אוּר <span class=\"dh-divergent\">מעיקר&#x27;</span></b> כולהו עבדי מעשה",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 34a:6:4",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "כדפרישי': <b>דְּאַיְיתִי אוּר לְבַסּוֹף</b> איהו הוא דעבד והנך לא עבדי מידי:",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 34a:6:5",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b><span class=\"dh-divergent\">בקדירה</span> חֲדָשָׁה עָסְקִינַן</b> שנותנין אותה רקנית על האור לחסמה:",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 34a:7:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>וּמִשּׁוּם לִבּוּן רְעָפִים נָגְעוּ בָּהּ</b> משום הך גזירה גופה שאסרו ללבן",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 34a:7:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "רעפים נגעו גם בזו: <b>חֲדָשִׁים</b> וכ\"ש ישנים: <b>הרי</b> <b>הן</b> <b>ככל</b> <b>הכלים</b> <b>הנטלין.</b> בשבת בחצר דחזו למיתב בגוייהו מידי: <b>אין</b> <b>סכין</b> <b>אותן</b> <b>שמן.</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 34a:8:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "להחליקן ולצחצחן: <b>טָשִׁין</b> שפין: <b>ואין</b> <b>מפיגין</b> <b>אותן.</b> לאחר הסקן אין מפיגין הסקן בצונן לחסמן שמתקשין ע\"י הצונן וכולהו משום דמתקן",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 34a:8:4",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "מנא: <b>וְאִם</b> להפיגה בשביל לאפות שהוסקו הרבה וחושש שלא תשרף הפת מותר: <b>מולגין.</b> ברותחין: <b>אין</b> <b>טופלין</b> <b>אותן.</b> בסיד להסיר",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 34a:8:6",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "שערן דהוי דרך העבדנין: <b>וְאֵין גּוֹזְזִין אוֹתָן בְּמִסְפָּרַיִם</b> דמחזי כצריך לשער: <b>ואין</b> <b>גוזזין</b> <b>הירק.</b> התלוש שיש בו ראשי עלין נרקבין",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 34a:9:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "וכמושין אין גוזזין אותן בתספורת שלו שגוזזין בה מן המחובר דמאן דחזי סבר שלקטן היום: <b><span class=\"dh-divergent\">קונדס</span> <span class=\"dh-divergent\">ועכביות</span></b> מיני ירקות הן שיש",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 34a:10:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        9
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "טורח בתקונן: <b><span class=\"dh-divergent\">פורני</span></b> הן תנורים שלנו הגדולים ופיהם בצדם ולא חיישינן לטרחא אם יש לו אוכלין הרבה דלא סגי ליה בתנור: <b>שמא</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 34a:10:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        9
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>תִּפָּחֵת</b> ע\"י שחדשה היא ונמצא טורח שלא לצורך: <b>אין</b> <b>נופחין</b> <b>במפוח.</b> דמחזי כאומן עושה מלאכה: <b>ואין</b> <b>מתקנין</b> <b>את</b> <b>השפוד.</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 34a:10:4",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        9
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ודלא כר' יהודה אי נמי בנרצם מערב י\"ט ודברי הכל: <b>אֵין מְפַצְּעִין אֶת הַקָּנֶה</b> לתת קרומיותיו תחת המליח על האסכלא",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 34a:11:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        10
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "שעושה כלי דכל מידי דעביד להשתמש בו הוי תקון כלי: <b>וְאֵין חוֹשְׁשִׁין שֶׁמָּא תִּקָּרַע</b> ואפי' נקרעת לא אכפת לן דאין זה קורע על",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 34a:11:4",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        10
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "מנת לתפור: <b>מַתְנִי׳ וְעוֹד אָמַר <span class=\"dh-divergent\">ר&#x27;</span> אֱלִיעֶזֶר.</b> משום דתנא אחת לקולא גבי מוקצה והדר אמר אחריתי קאמר ועוד וקשיא לי בגוה והא",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 34a:12:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        11
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "אפסקוה רבנן במילי טובא באין מוציאין את האור והנך דבהדיה והיינו מלתא אחריתי דלאו מלתיה ואמאי לא אותביניה בעירובין (<a href=\"/eruvin/23a\">דף כג.</a>)",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 34a:12:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        11
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "גבי ועוד דר' יהודה בן בבא דאותביה מר\"א דסוכה ושנינן לא אפסקוה אלא במלתיה ואלו אותבינה מהא לא הוה ליה לשנויי הכי ואומר אני",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 34a:12:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        11
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "שגרסת המשנה שלא כסדר: <b>עוֹמֵד אָדָם עַל הַמּוּקְצֶה.</b> הצריך הזמנה והזמנה מועלת לו כגון אחזי ולא אחזי דאמר באין צדין (<a href=\"/beitzah/26b\">לעיל ביצה דף כו:</a>):",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Beitzah 34a:12:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        11
      ]
    }
  ],
